data.description:
Lovely Beaver Lake home situated on wooded lot.  Kitchen has been updated with stainless steel appliances, new cabinets, and new flooring throughout home. Main level has 2 bedrooms. Loft has bedroom with 3/4 bath. Finished  basement has room for an office or bedroom and boasts a spacious rec room with another 3/4 bath and laundry. Deck has wonderful lake views. Home is within walking distance to beach, pool, clubhouse, park and marina. 
Virtual Tour Link https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=k39QVthz7nH
data.whatILove: Feels like a true lake home, nestled in the trees with a lake view and walking distance to the lake, pool, and marina.
